text: Jacob Andersson (born March 17, 1995) is a Swedish ice hockey defenceman. He is currently playing with Skellefteå AIK of the Swedish Hockey League (SHL). Andersson made his Swedish Hockey League debut playing with Skellefteå AIK during the 2014–15 SHL season. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Asplöven HC players Category:IF Björklöven players Category:Skellefteå AIK players Category:Swedish ice hockey defencemen Category:VIK Västerås HK players
